"""Test get_storage_resource_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_storage_resource_stats(storage_resource_id=self.
    p_data.storage_resource_id, storage_container_id=self.p_data.
    storage_resource_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now, end_time
    =self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.STORAGE_RES))
